What moves while scrolling
State 1 / Page 1
Big logo sits centered, very large.
Intro sentence is at the top center.
Event info is near the bottom.
White sticky footer/nav is fixed at bottom: PROGRAMMA left, TICKETS right.
State 2 / Page 2
Event info moves to the very top.
Big logo moves slightly upward and overlays the manifesto text.
Manifesto text appears behind the logo.
Curated line appears near bottom.
Footer/nav stays fixed.
State 3 / Page 3
Logo becomes much smaller and moves to the top center.
Event info splits left and right around the logo.
Manifesto text is now fully readable in the center.
Brush underline stays under the manifesto.
Footer/nav still fixed.
State 4 / Page 4
Same layout as state 3.
Background color changes from pale yellow/green to soft peach/pink.
Content positions stay the same.
Footer/nav still fixed.
So the scroll animation is basically:
Hero poster → logo overlays text → logo shrinks to header → background color changes.
